{"tid":926347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人漢疑夥女乞丐呃錢　善心婦慘遭劫殺","createTime":"2018-12-03T11:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T14:02:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6b354c72dd995991ccb75b1ef8a9aefaf91b99","tid":926347,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181203/photo/bkn-20181203190326253-1203_00972_001_01p.jpg?20181203191443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20181203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181203190326253-1203_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20181203191443&h=0bed4781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">史密絲（左圖）在右圖的街口遇上女乞丐。 （互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n美國馬里蘭州巴爾的摩一名女子，上周六（1日）凌晨見到一名女子在街上行乞，好心之下決定慷慨解囊，豈料一名男子突然上前搶其錢包，用刀刺傷女子胸口後逃去。女子送院後不治，警方正通緝行兇者及該名女乞丐，懷疑兩人是同謀。<br />\n<br />\n52歲的史密絲（Jacquelyn Smith）當日剛參加完家庭聚會，親戚接載她回家。途中她見到一名年約20多歲的黑人女子，手持寫上「請施捨讓我可以餵孩子」的紙板，懷中看似抱着一名嬰兒。她動了惻隱之心，絞下車窗遞錢給該女子。<br />\n<br />\n此時，年約30餘歲的黑人男子走上前向史密絲道謝，之後突然伸手入車內，試圖搶她的錢包。兩人爭持間，男子亮刀刺向史密絲胸部，然後與女乞丐一同逃去；史密絲送院搶救，惜最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181203/bkn-20181203190326253-1203_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20181203%2Fbkn-20181203190326253-1203_00972_001.html&d=HDF4iqn3TsE2X21HJ8eDoP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=2d7eaef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181203/bkn-20181203190326253-1203_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e3b9616edd04c9dbb81a418afdf23a9bd322f2dd","tid":926347,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"Nigger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad3191e85f01e5a46bb565e9ba3f32b84c0466a","tid":926347,"uid":179810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"黑人vs黑人 點開盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8225971734fad046422ee4787c7484d0a3752bc8","tid":926347,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}